{"tid":1696666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★旅業倡資助市民$120本地遊　助業界有工開","createTime":"2019-11-06T09:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T14:56:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"63e40e2ddb743ca5c0c2b5d0f004b27857b4ca00","tid":1696666,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"反修例示威嚴重打擊旅遊業，政府推出3輪紓困措施，但未能紓緩業界困境。香港旅遊業工會決定自救，反建議推出「香港人遊香港」計劃，由政府為參加旅行團的香港市民津貼120港元，市民可用最低<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>50港元參加香港一日遊</strong></span>，幫助旅遊業「有工開」之餘，讓市民遊覽香港紓解悶氣。<br />\n香港旅遊聯業工會聯會、香港專業導遊總工會、飲食業職工總會、百貨商業僱員總會今日(6日)舉行記者會，向政府建議實施「香港人遊香港」計劃。旅遊聯業工會聯會理事長梁芳遠介紹初步構思，以政府撥款1億港元、每人資助120港元計算，半年可有80萬香港市民受惠，若每團50人，旅行社能組織約1.6萬個團，並一併帶動導遊、旅遊車司機及酒樓食肆等各行業的生計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191106/bkn-20191106152856071-1106_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191106%2Fbkn-20191106152856071-1106_00822_001.html&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX79EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=564c2f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191106/bkn-20191106152856071-1106_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c9f83de66268ef7ec0b60231e7d2c80540e0838","tid":1696666,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"TG scene一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb68d4107d4af092aa6d19134004ca87837df3a","tid":1696666,"uid":184488,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁不如直接派錢啦咁撚多爹"},{"pid":"9998e91c7c1bfe8620d516bfc45107476a1e5906","tid":1696666,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"去邊遊好？"},{"pid":"657bd310190a750672feaa4514ac2e8251b2ccf6","tid":1696666,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0